translate English day9_1b202e1e:


    "\n I woke up feeling the most okay I've felt in a while."


translate English day9_26cfc335:


    "Up until now, things have been going so well with no thanks to me that I couldn't help but feel anxious, uncomfortable, and on edge, as if waiting for some mystery second shoe to drop."


translate English day9_ff096fad:


    "My chat with the sister the other day gave me a lot to think about, however, and I came to realize none of that was necessary."


translate English day9_edf01878:


    et "Why is it that the most arrogant monkeys are the first to fall from their treetop perches?"


translate English day9_5d299d24:



    nvl clear
    "\n The angel did not show up in my dreams today."


translate English day9_fbfa33bf:


    "The morning sun greets, sprawled out on my soft, spacious bed with a sweat drenched brow. {w}Clearly I'd dreamed of something, but I couldn't remember what exactly."


translate English day9_5398dc71:


    "The realization of where I am is comforting in its insignificant normalcy."


translate English day9_5f417fab:


    et "This place is incomparable to the Cleanup Department's dorms, the ever present musk in the air testament to the mold that's seeped into the woodwork."


translate English day9_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_02b5e636:


    "\n I give my face a good scrubbing using the hot water from the from the sink before checking out my face in the mirror, {w}unmarred by cracks here and there in the glass."


translate English day9_475dab33:


    "Come to think of it, I haven't taken a good look at my own face in quite some time."


translate English day9_6c63514f:


    "Relief flows through me on seeing I look far better than I'd anticipated, {w}which is when I notice a mark around my neck where the collar of my shirt would normally be."


translate English day9_3f398f64:


    et "Its location is such that it would be completely hidden under my usual attire. {w}I notice faint bruising around the edges."


translate English day9_174079d5:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"If you come here again, seeking out a being you do not truly understand,"


translate English day9_c2accd04:


    extend " you will die. Not by the hands of God, but by the power of Pestis itself.\""


translate English day9_93476809:


    "My memories of the events from the past night jolt me back to reality, like getting hit in the head. {w}It'd been so utterly bizarre that I'd mistakenly thought it was a dream."


translate English day9_03218bb0:


    "I wonder if Bishop Haku is truly okay, harboring such a frightening force inside of herself?"


translate English day9_e146a122:


    "My mind replays what she told me the night before. {w}It's clear that she is out for blood from at least one person."


translate English day9_b9985c52:


    "\"We'll start with the emperor of the Magic Department's daughter, that peculiar monk mage, {w}and throw in those ancient temple elders who somehow seem to avoid death, clinging to their useless reign for far too long."


translate English day9_a16d9b46:


    et "Depending on what happens, perhaps even some of my feeble lambs and that girl you like so much will return with me to the beginning of the world, {w}to rejoin their mothers from whence they came.\""


translate English day9_c42b5b39:



    nvl clear
    "\n Her use of the phrase, \"that girl you like so much,\" makes me wonder if she somehow knows about what happened between Maya and myself."


translate English day9_3ae382f8:


    "It scares me. {w}My confrontation yesterday was impulsive, and thinking back, I clearly stumbled into something that I should have remained in the dark about."


translate English day9_f2ffcd40:


    "How much can I possibly and realistically do against the embodiment of Pestis itself?"


translate English day9_192b2982:


    "Should I tell someone? {w}I probably shouldn't."


translate English day9_bb56a85c:


    "I get the feeling she knows I'll either keep my shut about what happened, {w}or that it'll sound so bizarre, no one will ever believe me."


translate English day9_e9d0a559:


    et "Otherwise, she wouldn't have spouted such delusional sounding bullshit to me, a priest in the temple. {w}I turn off the tap. My head's full of convoluted thoughts."


translate English day9_ceac9b7a:



    nvl clear
    "\n I still can't focus properly on my new life, and now, a new and dangerous problem rears its ugly head, causing even more mental chaos."


translate English day9_81be0fc1:


    et "Is it my insatiable curiosity that's the reason behind why bad things keep happening to me, one after another? {w}No, it has to be the mysterious nature of that place."


translate English day9_76b2fe88_2:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_0f04dbf8:


    "\n The Cleanup Department is rotten to the core. {w}They've gotten to the point where they've forgotten to look out for themselves."


translate English day9_5f1d2b89:


    "It's an absurd notion--and a job that everyone detests."


translate English day9_d0a09aaa:


    "There is no way that kids who have only just attained adulthood could remain sane when such things happen endlessly, over and over."


translate English day9_754e6626:


    "The funniest thing of all is how I can look back on that absurd accident that befell me only yesterday with such cool detachment."


translate English day9_23a1a98d:


    "And that's not the most horrifying thing of all."


translate English day9_e3fc5235:


    et "What makes it all the more frightening is how, the longer one works there, the more normal that kind of thing becomes."


translate English day9_72878988:



    nvl clear
    "\n You become numb to the unfair treatment you receive, day after day, {w}and each cruel incident you experience only drives you closer to violence."


translate English day9_7d57192d:


    "The only way they can cope is by bullying people around them and putting themselves down."


translate English day9_6c696763:


    "I thought about what I had done to deserve the treatment I'd received. {w}Something that would have caused those other priests to treat me that way, some aspect of myself that was lacking."


translate English day9_643e402e:


    "But there's no point agonizing over it. {w}Because I'm doing more harm to myself as I spiral into my head, like the snowball effect."


translate English day9_f0d19e46:


    "The more I think about it, the more trivial it becomes, though a part of me resents myself for only realizing it now."


translate English day9_0f216e1e:


    et "I hadn't been able to see things for what they were while enmeshed in that rotten department. {w}But now that I'm a few steps away, everything has become far more clear."


translate English day9_49f32361:



    nvl clear
    "\n Is this what Securett has been trying to warn me about this whole time?"


translate English day9_e6be044b:


    "Considering how complicated things have so quickly become, {w}I can see how impossible it would have been to explain the situation succinctly using words alone."


translate English day9_c929c5d9:


    "Maya's different, though. As certainty becomes fact, my concern for her only grows stronger."


translate English day9_afcd462a:


    "A part of me wonders how long I can safely leave her in a place like that."


translate English day9_33eeb503:


    et "She mentioned wanting to move to the Health Department. {w}Maybe I can follow up on that and figure out what's necessary for her to do so."


translate English day9_76b2fe88_3:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_6f734b5d:


    nar "The fact that no one from within the Cleanup Department really knows me well is a huge weight off my shoulders."


translate English day9_a317779b:


    nar "I still need some time to get used to my new life here in the Magic Department and the strict rules they have in place, {w}but I'm confident that won't take me too much longer."


translate English day9_40d8fc4a:


    nar "Bits and pieces of my forgotten past float through my mind, one after another. {w}Though it's not necessarily a bad feeling."


translate English day9_8325019d:


    pl "Yo! Arnie!"


translate English day9_b73d09ba:


    ar "Ah, Brother [na]. You're looking well today. I'm glad to see it."


translate English day9_ae298767:


    nar "I call out a friendly greeting as I approach the sister. {w}The priests around her look over at me with surprise and envy."


translate English day9_3d07fb17:


    nar "I've experienced this before, though it feels far different compared to being referred to as The Outsider."


translate English day9_1f994dc6:


    nar "It only further highlights the glaring difference between departments, {w}with the folks here retaining a higher social status and having received a proper education."


translate English day9_25699b29:


    nar "Though even with my history with the Cleanup Department, I'm nothing more than a trainee with only two stigmata."


translate English day9_81eb31fd:


    nar "I have to figure out where I'm going first if I don't want to cause trouble for myself before I've even started."


translate English day9_d99bedff:


    pl "I appreciate the advice you gave me yesterday. {w}I feel a lot better now thanks to you, Sister."


translate English day9_9a49c01a:


    pl "I'm also sorry for all the trouble I caused."


translate English day9_5bc55d18:


    ar "There's no need for that. What are you apologizing for? {w}I should be thanking you for giving me a chance to get my thoughts in order."


translate English day9_adf7183f:


    ar "Besides, it's almost like a dream come true, being able to exchange good mornings with you like this!"


translate English day9_bd25a19d:


    ar "And for you to say such sweet things on top of that! I should be the one thanking you."


translate English day9_7c35e1e2:


    pl "Mm, that's going a little overboard. {w}As the auxiliary bishop to the Magic Department, you have a natural born gift, not only with your work, but with your interpersonal relationships as well."


translate English day9_49f285fc:


    ar "I only speak the truth, you know."


translate English day9_2ee6f74b:


    nar "Of course it's true. {w}And she's right. There's no doubt the experience I gain here will only help me in the future."


translate English day9_5b05f437:


    nar "I need to absorb as much information as I can so I'll be able to at least exist in the capital if or when my stay here in the temple ends."


translate English day9_55ae1d36:


    nar "Everything is slowly but firmly falling into place. {w}It's been a long time coming."


translate English day9_a8e89cb7:


    nar "That's right. I have to keep on doing what I can. {w}My once dismantled pride is completely restored in the blink of an eye though I regret acting so out of sorts on my first day."


translate English day9_2d567817:


    nar "This isn't a sudden stroke of good luck falling fortuitously into my lap. {w}It's more like the good fortune I should have kept safe from the beginning finally returning to me."


translate English day9_f37f44c0:


    nar "Those naive priests here in the department are creeped out by my more liberal attitude {w}while feeling envious of the favoritism the bishop and auxiliary bishop so blatantly shower on me."


translate English day9_b9c6c9ba:


    nar "I'm sure the creeps on the Disposal Team felt the same exact way."


translate English day9_2ffb5d0d:


    nar "Sorry, guys, but I'm just too amazing! {w}I can't help but laugh at the thought alone."


translate English day9_b953f5be:


    pl "Heh heh! The hardest part was getting into the Magic Department, but now I can relax a bit."


translate English day9_a286badb:


    ar "Oh! I'm glad to hear you say that. {w}I find myself to be fairly boring as far as leaders go, and yet I always end up putting everyone on edge without meaning to."


translate English day9_0f7c0de9:


    ar "Maybe you can help me think up a solution to this problem of mine."


translate English day9_4dc90020:


    pl "Ulp... I meant that as a lighthearted joke so you could scold me slightly..."


translate English day9_9c23cf0e:


    nar "The more awkward things get, the harder I find it is to crack jokes."


translate English day9_e895c8be:


    nar "I've received a lot of help from Arnie, and seeing her look at me like that makes me slightly guilty for my pretentious opinions."


translate English day9_cb5b7dbf:


    nar "What more can I do for this woman who's already done so much for me? {w}Other than simply working hard at my job."


translate English day9_0ccc8475:


    en "What do you think you're doing, buddying up to my sister at this ungodly hour?"


translate English day9_0db91657:


    pl "There he is! That's the guy who I know will give me a stern talking to!"


translate English day9_600e0839:


    pl "If you're that jealous, why not take my place and get cozy with her yourself?"


translate English day9_ad09cbe3:


    en "H-How dare you say something so outrageous!"


translate English day9_8f641f14:


    ar "What's so outrageous about it?"


translate English day9_437626ac:


    en "Y-You've got it all wrong, sister... I didn't mean it like that..."


translate English day9_177de121:


    pl "Your brother is kind of a monster."


translate English day9_0a6994c9:


    en "Hey! Stop teasing your brother!"


translate English day9_e7f81969:


    pl "Hee hee!"


translate English day9_13228515:


    nar "From such a high vantage point, one can easily see the surrounding landscape at a single glance. {w}Lights twinkle here and there underneath the gloomy sky."


translate English day9_8f9d470a:


    nar "Although the brightest light of all comes from the temple smack-dab in the middle of it all--Saint Sheol."


translate English day9_eb11b3e0:


    nar "It's often said that those who live outside the capital come up with the wildest of tales based on this light."


translate English day9_03a76150:


    nar "I wish I, too, could see that light as purely a thing of beauty, but I'm not so lucky."


translate English day9_4f6d139a:


    nar "Several abandoned houses, filled to the brim with junk. {w}A veritable mountain of trash."


translate English day9_ea22feed:


    nar "Black puddles full of rot drain into the nearby river. {w}I wonder how many corpses are buried just underneath, hidden by the fog?"


translate English day9_de9409e9:


    nar "Amidst the ant-like people scurrying to and fro, I spot a peculiar sight. {w}Something appears to be crawling out of the entrance to a cave."


translate English day9_fb5960bf:


    nar "The reason why it stands out even from such a great distance is because the figure is not alone."


translate English day9_6f646572:


    nar "I wonder how many people, how many dozens of people are frozen like that, as they crawl out from inside the cave?"


translate English day9_a341edfe:


    nar "They move sluggishly yet quickly, leaving streaks of blood behind themselves."


translate English day9_14219ec9:


    nar "As I peer out, huddled once more in front of the window, there's once again nothing."


translate English day9_eaa4de24:


    nar "It's enough to fill me with a despondent emptiness. I place my hot forehead against the cool windowpane to calm my thoughts."


translate English day9_8fb1e7c7:


    nar "Which is when someone calls my name from immediately behind me."


translate English day9_be869bc2:


    nar "The folks within the Magic Department, who revere acting as a group whenever possible, {w}usually file into work in the morning as a single unit."


translate English day9_1fc0a3b1:


    nar "I followed along with it at first, not wanting to ruin the rhythm of our synchronized footsteps."


translate English day9_27a1ca6b:


    nar "The priests all decked out in pure black habits are the like the epitome of punctuality and meticulousness itself as they walk along quietly in single file."


translate English day9_4c176334:


    nar "Unable to bear the silence, I immediately open my mouth as soon as I step out of my room."


translate English day9_92c7bb7f:


    pl "So, what are we doing today?"


translate English day9_f73d0a4b:


    ar "I was planning on giving you a simple demonstration on how we contain instances of Pestis."


translate English day9_bd93e3df:


    en "To be honest, neither myself nor my sister really need to be here, but I have business nearby so I figured we could tag along."


translate English day9_96840f4e:


    pl "I didn't realize the Magic Department operated outside the temple."


translate English day9_16e5180e:


    en "We sure do. Actually, the only departments that do are the Magic Department and the Cleanup crew."


translate English day9_99b672d0:


    en "In fact, we sometimes work together."


translate English day9_bddd4b1e:


    pl "Really? {w}That's the first I've heard of it. What sort of stuff do you guys do?"


translate English day9_b3e59ed4:


    en "Nothing complicated. {w}Evil spirits can sometimes linger even after the bodies have been cleaned up, and the Magic Department doesn't have enough manpower to deal with them all."


translate English day9_76ac28da:


    en "The Cleanup Department has basically always acted as backup troops."


translate English day9_680900cd:


    pl "I do remember hearing about that. {w}Is that why the Cleanup Department is sometimes referred to as the Disposal Team?"


translate English day9_a5f61ce3:


    en "Mmm..."


translate English day9_bfd31352:


    nar "Enoch glances over at his sister, and as if trying to read her expression."


translate English day9_b1081d8d:


    nar "After confirming that she's looking straight ahead and not paying attention to us, {w}he discretely leans over, whispering in my ear."


translate English day9_809d40a3:


    en "The priests in the Magic Department still have a tendency to look down on the folks in the Cleanup Department. {w}That said, I personally think it's in both of our interests to stay on good terms with them..."


translate English day9_c4e8d455:


    pl "Sounds fair enough, but why are you whispering?"


translate English day9_ba35d329:


    en "I don't want my sister overhearing anything she doesn't need to."


translate English day9_c9714055:


    pl "Huh? That seems pretty overprotective. {w}Your sister isn't a child, you know..."


translate English day9_77b6c659:


    pl "Besides, shouldn't the bishop be the first one to know about this kind of stuff?"


translate English day9_20bbf672:


    en "Clearly, there's still a lot you don't know about the bishop, [na], if you're saying stuff like that..."


translate English day9_9ea90ecf:


    en "Even though she may come off as such to you, [na], I strongly advise you to consider your words more carefully."


translate English day9_dbe6e2d9:


    pl "It might not be my place to say, but I have a feeling you're in the same boat."


translate English day9_394dbbc2:


    nar "That's right. {w}The only reason he can act so carefree about the department is due to his lack of knowledge about it."


translate English day9_6f88d5a2:


    nar "Though the realization only hammers in the truth about how vastly different the Magic Department is from the Cleanup Department."


translate English day9_f5c0a4be:


    nar "And likewise, the Disposal Team will doesn't have a chance in hell of understanding the Magic Department."


translate English day9_0bf45cfc:


    nar "The world is full of all sorts of people, their actions and behavior remaining an eternal mystery no matter what you do."


translate English day9_5b0942d9:


    nar "With that in mind, I wonder if the two departments will ever be able to see eye to eye? {w}From where I'm standing, it definitely won't be easy."


translate English day9_848bbc46:


    nar "It's not that anyone in particular is to blame, either. {w}Which only makes things more difficult."


translate English day9_dbe1fe3b:


    en "At any rate, I just want everyone to get along. {w}Which is why we need less of what happened yesterday, [na]. Got it?"


translate English day9_24e5f8b0:


    pl "You're still holding a grudge about that? {w}Fine, fine. Just stop getting on my case about it. {w}Let's coexist in peaceful harmony."


translate English day9_fba82e51:


    nar "It's clear he's once again skeptical of me. {w}When will I ever be seen as something other than The Outsider around here?"


translate English day9_d1711eb2:


    nar "To be fair, that's not really what I want. {w}I'd be happy just becoming a little more used to my new life."


translate English day9_c1d3dfbc:


    nar "Then perhaps I won't need to be plagued by any more freaky dreams or hallucinations."


translate English day9_23dcb55f:


    nar "And then I won't need to feel so on edge all the time."


translate English day9_76d0a4bf:


    nar "As I lose myself in thought, the group's steady pace gradually slows to a crawl."


translate English day9_78d5a7c0:


    nar "It seems like we're going underground. {w}I can hear the surreptitious sound of water flowing, as if we're in some kind of cave."


translate English day9_1755ad4b:


    pl "Where are we?"


translate English day9_77c6b620:


    nar "I look around our current location anxiously."


translate English day9_df4789ff:


    nar "I have a feeling we're in that mysterious cave I spotted earlier, although I can't be sure since it was so far away."


translate English day9_9eceb424:


    ar "What's the matter, Brother [na2]?"


translate English day9_bb756fd9:


    nar "Glancing over at the bishop once more, I realize how silly I was to worry."


translate English day9_e8c1e3a4:


    nar "I'm with the Magic Department now, not the Disposal Team. {w}Not only that, but by my side..."


translate English day9_e560761f:


    nar "...stands the Magic Department's very own auxiliary bishop, Arne Alternata."


translate English day9_4c3aab95:


    nar "I'm embarrassed that I allowed myself to get that worried, even just a little."


translate English day9_19ddc28f:


    pl "It's nothing. Let's hurry up and get in."


translate English day9_7f5f1280:


    ar "Of course. The floor is slippery, so be sure to watch your step."


translate English day9_bb7cd012:


    nar "The single file procession of priests, all with their lamps held before them to help illuminate the pitch black path ahead, is eerie."


translate English day9_6f1a1a11:


    nar "The cave itself is almost viciously humid, feeling hot compared to how cold it is outside."


translate English day9_6b26f55c:


    nar "With summers in the capital being quite cold, it's been a while since I experienced such high humidity and heat. {w}The warmth enveloping my body quickly raises my body temperature."


translate English day9_0d8315b8:


    pl "This is probably a dumb question, but can you actually vanquish Pestis?"


translate English day9_be9f70cd:


    ar "Mm, not exactly vanquish entirely... {w}More like placing it in a form of stasis."


translate English day9_a3041936:


    ar "Pestis itself is essentially a form of divine punishment from God, making it impossible to eliminate by human power alone."


translate English day9_268bcce9:


    pl "How exactly do you put it to rest?"


translate English day9_35b87905:


    ar "Those afflicted by Pestis are considerably weaker than normal. {w}They tend to feel a slight amount of vertigo and their surroundings appear slightly darker than usual."


translate English day9_b58abb55:


    pl "Seriously? So you're saying it'd be easy enough to run circles around them?"


translate English day9_55f0172a:


    ar "There is no need to worry. {w}Once a human becomes used to the presence of Pestis, it basically is no longer aware of those around it."


translate English day9_88d5da12:


    pl "Stop freaking me out!"


translate English day9_89ceadd5:


    ar "I am Arne Alternata, the teller of kindhearted jokes."


translate English day9_c4a69b54:


    pl "You really need to work on your delivery..."


translate English day9_e2ad5aad:


    ar "Y-You really think so? {w}I'll do better next time."


translate English day9_d00d0ff9:


    pl "If you keep this up, your brother's gonna get angry at me for teaching you weird things."


translate English day9_318de931:


    ar "I was joking earlier, but the fact remains unchanged. As beings below God, it is impossible for us to eliminate the effects of their punishment completely."


translate English day9_199e26a4:


    ar "God punished them for a reason, after all."


translate English day9_f5a44463:


    ar "And to suffer that punishment is part of the karmic burden us humans must bear for living here on this earth."


translate English day9_e0c1ca3a:


    pl "I guess so, but the Pestis is killing off the soil as well, and... {w}Actually, never mind. I get it."


translate English day9_1c818677:


    nar "Mixed in with the stench of mud in the cave lies another peculiar scent. {w}It's slightly different from the smell I tend to associate with rotting bodies."


translate English day9_34868d33:


    nar "It's slightly sour, reminiscent of the dank, musky rot the reeks off the nearby bog. {w}Still, it's not a very good smell."


translate English day9_cf22c065:


    nar "Whether a direct effect from Pestis or not, the increasingly humid air is making it increasingly difficult for me to breathe, {w}my chest tightening from the effort."


translate English day9_d5298c73:


    nar "The moment it becomes too difficult for me to continue walking, a nearby priest calls out to the sister."


translate English day9_9f0e11dd:


    nar "Taking advantage of the moment, I gradually slow my pace to a literal crawl, and before long, I find myself at the back of the line."


translate English day9_663943bc:


    nar "As the trainee, I'll only get in the way by being near the front. Plus, I'm sure they'll call me if they need me."


translate English day9_0fc84fae:


    nar "The priest next to me leans over, shushing me quietly, and I look toward the front of the group."


translate English day9_147c0499:


    ar "Our Lord, author of the Holy Gospel and the source of life itself, hear our pleas!"


translate English day9_223c5258:


    nar "The group of priests, led by the sister herself, place their thumbs and pointer fingers together before repeating the words she just said."


translate English day9_0d99d3ba:


    nar "Oh Father, hallowed be thy name. {w}May your kingdom come. May your will be done on earth as it is in Heaven."


translate English day9_5c41b8e8:


    nar "Even I've heard these words once before. How do people remember this kind of stuff?"


translate English day9_3c02f7c8:


    nar "The sound of their voices resounding with an almost sublime serenity coupled with the hot, sticky air causes my eyelids to droop drowsily."


translate English day9_fbe0cbe4:


    nar "Everything started to go wrong when I let out an uncontrollable yawn. {w}It immediately sends the priest next to me into a laughing fit."


translate English day9_5a8903f3:


    ar "Do you find this amusing?"


translate English day9_eed348d8:


    ex6 "Uh... I-I don't..."


translate English day9_6f5cad4d:


    pl "Sorry, it's my fault. As a professional comedian, a joke came to mind that I just had to share."


translate English day9_256fb115:


    nar "I find myself speaking up on seeing her turn almost deathly pale."


translate English day9_6221f4e0:


    nar "Hearing me say something that ludicrous, several of the priests staring at me begin laughing themselves in response."


translate English day9_b40c1ced:


    nar "Whether or not this is yet another effect of their herd behavior, more and more priests begin joining in, the sounds of laughter bursting out sporadically within the group."


translate English day9_1b57d211:


    nar "As the atmosphere around us suddenly fills with hilarious delight, the two siblings exchange puzzled glances."


translate English day9_19aac93a:


    ar "I can't believe that even you guys are amused by this of all things."


translate English day9_df1369bb:


    ar "Come, come. The lot of you are well beyond the age of acting like bold-faced brats."


translate English day9_da7290f2:


    ar "Okay, let's get ourselves under control, everyone. Then we'll start over from the beginning."


translate English day9_2a004ca2:


    nar "I absently smooth down my hair, feeling slightly guilty, while keeping an eye on Arnie who has a small smile on her face. {w}I guess she's not actually that upset."


translate English day9_e779829a:


    nar "I spoiled the mood entirely, though I didn't mean to. {w}Thank goodness she's so accommodating."


